==Introduction==
旧式化した「九七艦攻」の後継機として開発された、新型の艦上攻撃機「天山」。<br>
機動部隊に配備され、主に雷撃任務を担当します。<br>
急降下爆撃機の｢彗星｣などと一緒に、ぜひ空母機動部隊で運用してくださいね。

''Developed as the successor of the obsolete "[[Type 97 Torpedo Bomber|Type 97 torpedo bomber]]", the new carrier-based attack aircraft "Tenzan".''<br>
''When deployed in a mobile-squadron, it is mainly responsible for fast-strike missions.''<br>
''Together with the "[[Suisei (Comet)|Suisei]]" dive bomber, please operate it as part of your aircraft carrier mobile squadron.''

